    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep small parts, crafts, or minerals organized with a Universal Hobby Aluminum Storage Container Set! The Universal Hobby Aluminum Storage Container Sets are a great addition to any craft set or hobby station. Featuring either 12, 15 or 20 aluminum containers with clear glass lids, you?ll be able to organize all of your small items. Each case uses a twist off lid so you can safely secure those small parts. Because the top is constructed of clear glass, you&#039;ll easily be able to tell your items apart without having to label the containers. These sets make for a great gift for crafters and hobbyists alike!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Universal Hobby Aluminum Storage Display Container Set and Case (Various Packs)</h2>\n  <p>Keep small parts, crafts, or minerals organized with a Universal Hobby Aluminum Storage Container Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Dimensions of 12pc Cases:</strong> </li>\n    <li>2&quot; Diameter, 7/8&quot; Deep</li>\n    <li><strong>Dimensions of 15pc Cases:</strong> </li>\n    <li>1 3/8&quot; Diameter, 7/8&quot; Deep</li>\n    <li><strong>Dimensions of 20pc Cases:</strong> </li>\n    <li>1 1/4&quot; Diameter, 3/4&quot; Deep</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 1